PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781880484
OL,3,CBurnham's Makerfield by-election win
OL,4,Cspells end for Starmer as prime
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FBurnham's allies are encouraging the
OL,8,Fprime minister to talk to him in the
OL,9,Fcoming days.
OL,11,FIt will be the first conversation
OL,12,Fbetween the pair since a very brief
OL,13,Fchat at the start of the by-election.
OL,15,FThe aim is to persuade Keir Starmer to
OL,16,Fset out a timetable for his departure,
OL,17,Fto leave office in a dignified manner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
