PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781880484
OL,3,CBurnham's Makerfield by-election win
OL,4,Cspells end for Starmer as prime
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FThe prime minister insists he is going
OL,8,Fnowhere, but the thumping majority
OL,9,Fdelivered by Makerfield's voters may
OL,10,Fshake his resolve.
OL,12,FBurnham's team believe Wes Streeting,
OL,13,Fanother leadership hopeful, will
OL,14,Fconclude he has no hope of beating
OL,15,FMakerfield's new MP in a leadership
OL,16,Fcontest and will soon offer his
OL,17,Fsupport.
OL,19,FThe former health secretary met
OL,20,Fprivately with Andy Burnham in
OL,21,FMakerfield earlier this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
