PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781880484
OL,3,CBurnham's Makerfield by-election win
OL,4,Cspells end for Starmer as prime
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FSome backers of Streeting are expected
OL,8,Fto switch sides to Burnham over the
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FFor Reform, this result poses
OL,12,Fchallenges, too.
OL,14,FThere are questions about their
OL,15,Fcandidate selection; there are
OL,16,Fquestions about whether the party can
OL,17,Fbeat a Burnham-led Labour party; there
OL,18,Fare questions about where Nigel Farage
OL,19,Fand his party have peaked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
