OL,3,CBurnham's Makerfield by-election win
OL,4,Cspells end for Starmer as prime
OL,5,Cminister
OL,7,FAndy Burnham's journey is two-thirds
OL,8,Fcomplete. He has found himself a seat.
OL,9,FHe has won a by-election. The final
OL,10,Fhurdle may end up being the easiest
OL,11,Fyet.
OL,13,FOnce the journey to Number 10 is
OL,14,Ffinished, he will need to demonstrate
OL,15,Fa credible plan for government.
OL,17,FThe voters of Makerfield, Labour MPs
OL,18,Fand the general public all expect
OL,19,Ftheir own version of the change
OL,20,Fpromised by Burnham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
